Article.ArticleTitle: Plant-derived triterpenoids and analogues as antitumor and anti-HIV agents.

AbstractText: This article reviews the antitumor and anti-HIV activities of naturally occurring triterpenoids, including the lupane, ursane, oleanane, lanostane, dammarane, and miscellaneous scaffolds. Structure–activity relationships of selected natural compounds and their synthetic derivatives are also discussed.
